575
00:32:29,090 --> 00:32:30,310
The thing is,

576
00:32:30,550 --> 00:32:32,820
as long as we don't obtain the
method of weapon forging,

577
00:32:32,820 --> 00:32:35,020
we have no way to fight against Nan Heng.

578
00:32:38,240 --> 00:32:39,030
That's true.

579
00:32:42,110 --> 00:32:43,720
Do you think in this world,

580
00:32:44,310 --> 00:32:47,240
there are truly fathers and sons
who hate each other?

581
00:32:48,880 --> 00:32:50,380
The method of weapon forging

582
00:32:50,380 --> 00:32:53,750
is the trump card His Majesty left for
the Eighteenth Prince to protect himself,

583
00:32:53,750 --> 00:32:55,610
but Nan Heng has always wanted to get it.

584
00:32:55,610 --> 00:32:56,570
Why is that?

585
00:32:58,660 --> 00:33:00,120
Because he wants to rebel.

586
00:33:01,840 --> 00:33:02,900
Rebellion

587
00:33:03,270 --> 00:33:04,000
means that

588
00:33:04,000 --> 00:33:05,640
many people will die.

589
00:33:05,970 --> 00:33:07,350
So even if I obtained

590
00:33:07,350 --> 00:33:08,460
this method of weapon forging,

591
00:33:08,460 --> 00:33:09,860
I wouldn't give it to him.

592
00:33:10,150 --> 00:33:11,560
How can you be so certain

593
00:33:11,660 --> 00:33:13,390
that he wants it for rebellion?

594
00:33:14,330 --> 00:33:16,330
Because it's written in the script.

595
00:33:18,040 --> 00:33:19,140
The script again.

596
00:33:20,310 --> 00:33:21,680
If he does plan to rebel,

597
00:33:22,710 --> 00:33:24,020
what do you plan to do?

598
00:33:28,890 --> 00:33:29,680
I don't know.

599
00:33:29,700 --> 00:33:31,300
I haven't made up my mind yet.

600
00:33:31,550 --> 00:33:34,280
Just stopping him is difficult enough
right now.

601
00:33:35,170 --> 00:33:37,410
But I still want to find another way,

602
00:33:37,760 --> 00:33:39,910
a way that can help Nan Heng

603
00:33:40,070 --> 00:33:41,510
let go of his hatred.

604
00:33:46,290 --> 00:33:47,440
Have you considered

605
00:33:48,710 --> 00:33:50,400
what if I told others

606
00:33:51,070 --> 00:33:52,930
about everything you've told me?

607
00:33:53,160 --> 00:33:54,420
What would you do then?

608
00:33:54,540 --> 00:33:55,670
That's impossible.

609
00:33:56,220 --> 00:33:57,720
You're Mr. Li.

610
00:34:01,310 --> 00:34:03,140
You're the person I trust

611
00:34:04,350 --> 00:34:05,510
most in this world.

612
00:34:18,960 --> 00:34:19,800
Miss Song.

613
00:34:20,889 --> 00:34:23,280
You can never truly know what's
in someone's heart.

614
00:34:23,280 --> 00:34:24,780
Being so quick to trust others

615
00:34:24,780 --> 00:34:26,710
will only end up hurting yourself.

616
00:34:27,460 --> 00:34:29,150
I am not a good person,

617
00:34:29,380 --> 00:34:30,670
nor am I

618
00:34:30,670 --> 00:34:32,730
the virtuous man you make me out to be.

619
00:34:33,510 --> 00:34:34,620
Mr. Li.

620
00:34:34,920 --> 00:34:37,230
I'm not someone who trusts others easily,

621
00:34:37,230 --> 00:34:38,360
but you're different.

622
00:34:38,360 --> 00:34:40,290
I'm no different from anyone else.

623
00:34:44,170 --> 00:34:45,170
In a moment,

624
00:34:45,199 --> 00:34:47,070
I'll have Shangguan He escort you back.

625
00:34:47,070 --> 00:34:49,800
I have matters to attend to, so I'll
take my leave.

626
00:34:50,270 --> 00:34:51,250
Mr. Li.

627
00:34:51,440 --> 00:34:52,320
Mr. Li!

628
00:34:56,270 --> 00:34:57,310
That's weird.

629
00:35:00,890 --> 00:35:02,330
What's gotten into him?

630
00:35:40,280 --> 00:35:41,080
Chief Master.

631
00:35:42,150 --> 00:35:43,480
I've escorted her back.

632
00:35:44,320 --> 00:35:45,420
Look at you.

633
00:35:45,590 --> 00:35:47,030
You're the one who drew her in,

634
00:35:47,030 --> 00:35:48,710
and you're the one pushing her away.

635
00:35:48,710 --> 00:35:50,370
What are you really thinking?

636
00:35:52,480 --> 00:35:53,540
Take a look at this.

637
00:35:57,190 --> 00:35:58,400
Isn't this that strange symbol

638
00:35:58,400 --> 00:35:59,880
from the method of weapon forging?

639
00:35:59,880 --> 00:36:00,880
She completed it?

640
00:36:01,760 --> 00:36:03,360
I didn't expect that either.

641
00:36:03,480 --> 00:36:04,680
However, this symbol

642
00:36:04,920 --> 00:36:07,780
differs from the one in the
Qianyu Military Manual,

643
00:36:07,800 --> 00:36:10,400
so it might not be the
method of weapon forging.

644
00:36:12,510 --> 00:36:13,110
Well then.

645
00:36:13,940 --> 00:36:14,890
I want you

646
00:36:14,910 --> 00:36:16,030
to go search for

647
00:36:16,030 --> 00:36:17,550
scholars across the land in secret
immediately

648
00:36:17,550 --> 00:36:20,150
to see if anyone recognizes
these characters.

649
00:36:21,590 --> 00:36:22,400
Understood.

650
00:36:23,230 --> 00:36:24,030
Hold on.

651
00:36:25,840 --> 00:36:26,630
I'm planning

652
00:36:26,760 --> 00:36:28,000
to hold the Qingtan Musical Banquet

653
00:36:28,000 --> 00:36:29,460
at Waning River Crescent.

654
00:36:29,710 --> 00:36:30,510
Why?

655
00:36:31,110 --> 00:36:32,770
These days, our Nightwalkers

656
00:36:32,960 --> 00:36:34,800
have been gathering information everywhere

657
00:36:34,800 --> 00:36:36,630
and searching for clues about the
method of weapon forging,

658
00:36:36,630 --> 00:36:38,630
which has consumed enormous funds.

659
00:36:38,630 --> 00:36:39,630
I originally intended

660
00:36:39,630 --> 00:36:41,590
to transfer funds from my mansion,

661
00:36:42,190 --> 00:36:44,030
but unfortunately, every outgoing
transaction of the mansion

662
00:36:44,030 --> 00:36:46,030
has to be monitored by the
Imperial Household Department,

663
00:36:46,030 --> 00:36:48,320
and every movement of funds
requires documentation

664
00:36:48,320 --> 00:36:49,190
and proof.

665
00:36:49,960 --> 00:36:50,960
So you want to use

666
00:36:50,960 --> 00:36:53,150
the opportunity of hosting the
Qingtan Musical Banquet

667
00:36:53,150 --> 00:36:54,630
to transfer funds here?

668
00:36:56,150 --> 00:36:56,880
Exactly.

669
00:36:57,550 --> 00:36:58,800
Do you know how big that banquet will be

670
00:36:58,800 --> 00:37:00,510
