671
00:37:00,510 --> 00:37:02,440
It will take a lot of time to prepare.

672
00:37:02,440 --> 00:37:03,710
And you know, those young masters

673
00:37:03,710 --> 00:37:05,710
and noble ladies are difficult
to deal with.

674
00:37:05,710 --> 00:37:08,110
Just thinking about it gives me
a headache.

675
00:37:08,180 --> 00:37:09,910
You should find another venue.

676
00:37:11,880 --> 00:37:12,680
Alright then.

677
00:37:14,120 --> 00:37:16,250
We can hold it at your mansion instead.

678
00:37:16,270 --> 00:37:19,000
Let's hold it at Waning River Crescent
after all.

679
00:37:23,480 --> 00:37:25,440
February 6th. Windy.

680
00:37:25,480 --> 00:37:27,480
The scent of plum blossoms carried
on the breeze.

681
00:37:27,480 --> 00:37:30,960
No desire to enjoy the fragrance,
thinking only of Miss Song.

682
00:37:31,670 --> 00:37:33,670
February 7th. Light rain.

683
00:37:33,670 --> 00:37:35,760
Raindrops tap against my lonely heart,

684
00:37:35,760 --> 00:37:39,150
yet nothing compares to Yiting's
gentle swaying steps.

685
00:37:39,150 --> 00:37:41,550
I miss you, Miss Song.

686
00:37:44,110 --> 00:37:45,710
Take these out and burn them,

687
00:37:45,760 --> 00:37:48,090
far away so they don't dirty my courtyard.

688
00:37:48,360 --> 00:37:49,150
Yes.

689
00:37:52,110 --> 00:37:53,510
Don't burn them.

690
00:37:54,110 --> 00:37:56,320
This time, I've inquired about it for you.

691
00:37:56,320 --> 00:37:57,550
The Eighteenth Prince will also attend

692
00:37:57,550 --> 00:37:59,320
the Qingtan Musical Banquet.

693
00:37:59,630 --> 00:38:02,710
You're skilled in poetry and music.

694
00:38:02,800 --> 00:38:04,320
Isn't this a heaven-sent

695
00:38:04,320 --> 00:38:07,650
opportunity to showcase yourself
in front of His Highness?

696
00:38:08,400 --> 00:38:10,230
What exactly do you take me for, Mother?

697
00:38:10,230 --> 00:38:12,280
Playing music, writing poetry,
showing off talents—

698
00:38:12,280 --> 00:38:14,310
am I just a plaything on stage
for others' amusement?

699
00:38:14,310 --> 00:38:16,400
What's the meaning of all this?

700
00:38:16,400 --> 00:38:19,110
Of course it has meaning!

701
00:38:19,320 --> 00:38:20,180
Think about it.

702
00:38:20,320 --> 00:38:22,230
If it weren't for these accomplishments,

703
00:38:22,230 --> 00:38:23,440
how could you possibly

704
00:38:23,440 --> 00:38:25,510
stand out among so many daughters

705
00:38:25,510 --> 00:38:26,700
from wealthy families

706
00:38:26,700 --> 00:38:28,310
and marry a noble husband?

707
00:38:29,290 --> 00:38:30,890
So my existence in this world

708
00:38:31,000 --> 00:38:32,800
is only for the sake of marriage?

709
00:38:33,150 --> 00:38:34,880
If not for marriage, then what?

710
00:38:35,000 --> 00:38:36,550
Don't tell me you want to take

711
00:38:36,550 --> 00:38:37,920
the imperial exams and become an official.

712
00:38:37,920 --> 00:38:39,000
Why not?

713
00:38:40,150 --> 00:38:41,360
Even if that were possible,

714
00:38:41,360 --> 00:38:43,110
you'd have to become the Empress first

715
00:38:43,110 --> 00:38:45,710
and have the Emperor change
the system for you.

716
00:38:52,190 --> 00:38:53,320
It will leave a scar.

717
00:38:54,690 --> 00:38:55,890
It won't leave a scar.

718
00:38:56,360 --> 00:38:57,400
Scar.

719
00:38:58,070 --> 00:38:58,760
No scar.

720
00:38:59,970 --> 00:39:01,400
Easy.

721
00:39:01,440 --> 00:39:02,920
It hurts so much, Xia.

722
00:39:03,650 --> 00:39:06,910
Better a moment of pain than
prolonged suffering, My Lady.

723
00:39:10,680 --> 00:39:12,820
He hadn't even finished applying
the ointment for me yet.

724
00:39:12,820 --> 00:39:14,970
Why did he suddenly leave?

725
00:39:16,000 --> 00:39:18,930
You're talking about Li Shiliu,
aren't you, My Lady?

726
00:39:22,960 --> 00:39:25,090
But what matters most right now

727
00:39:25,230 --> 00:39:27,230
isn't really Mr. Li's attitude.

728
00:39:28,670 --> 00:39:31,110
But My Lady, you'll have to marry
someone eventually.

729
00:39:31,110 --> 00:39:31,920
Before,

730
00:39:32,150 --> 00:39:34,550
