740
00:39:51,030 --> 00:39:52,190
"Exceptional Love."

741
00:39:52,190 --> 00:39:53,390
"Exceptional Love?"

742
00:39:54,150 --> 00:39:55,710
These past two days, the servants
in the mansion

743
00:39:55,710 --> 00:39:57,190
have been secretly passing it around,

744
00:39:55,770 --> 00:39:58,140
[Exceptional Love]

745
00:39:57,320 --> 00:39:59,630
