758
00:40:24,230 --> 00:40:25,430
full of dirty tricks.

759
00:40:25,710 --> 00:40:27,400
I'm telling you right now,

760
00:40:27,400 --> 00:40:29,070
if he's not behind this,

761
00:40:29,150 --> 00:40:30,550
I'll eat my hat.

762
00:40:30,880 --> 00:40:32,550
I knew these rumors couldn't be trusted.

763
00:40:32,550 --> 00:40:34,550
I know you only have Li Shiliu
in your heart, My Lady.

764
00:40:34,550 --> 00:40:35,840
Don't talk nonsense.

765
00:40:36,670 --> 00:40:38,870
