776
00:41:07,670 --> 00:41:09,000
Haven't I told you already?

777
00:41:09,000 --> 00:41:11,260
It's just a partnership, a partnership.

778
00:41:12,920 --> 00:41:13,920
That makes sense.

779
00:41:14,360 --> 00:41:16,030
How could you possibly like Mr. Li,
My Lady?

780
00:41:16,030 --> 00:41:17,550
