784
00:41:20,440 --> 00:41:21,570
bald and toothless.

785
00:41:21,840 --> 00:41:23,360
And if you think about it,

786
00:41:23,360 --> 00:41:24,800
he might be of poor character,

787
00:41:24,800 --> 00:41:26,320
robbing and killing, pillaging and
looting.

788
00:41:26,320 --> 00:41:26,710
He might even...

789
00:41:26,710 --> 00:41:27,510
Stop, stop.

790
00:41:27,880 --> 00:41:29,920
What nonsense are you talking about?

791
00:41:29,920 --> 00:41:31,480
He's upright and kind,

792
00:41:31,480 --> 00:41:32,670
loyal to his friends,

793
00:41:32,670 --> 00:41:34,150
tall and wealthy,

794
00:41:34,510 --> 00:41:35,570
and owns property.

795
00:41:36,320 --> 00:41:38,050
Although his job isn't stable,

796
00:41:38,110 --> 00:41:39,110
no matter what,

797
00:41:39,190 --> 00:41:40,550
he could be considered

798
00:41:40,760 --> 00:41:42,030
a small entrepreneur, right?

799
00:41:42,030 --> 00:41:43,320
You say you don't like him,

800
00:41:43,320 --> 00:41:45,280
but you can't stand hearing even
half a flaw about him.

801
00:41:45,280 --> 00:41:46,110
My Lady.

802
00:41:46,110 --> 00:41:48,320
You'll be turning 25 by spring.

803
00:41:48,510 --> 00:41:49,550
When do you plan

804
00:41:49,550 --> 00:41:51,510
to confess your feelings to Mr. Li?

805
00:41:51,510 --> 00:41:53,480
The wedding dress definitely has to be
the latest style.

806
00:41:53,480 --> 00:41:55,070
Should we choose the shop in the south

807
00:41:55,070 --> 00:41:56,110
or the one in the north of town?

808
00:41:56,110 --> 00:41:57,670
And the invitation cards, they must be...

809
00:41:57,670 --> 00:41:58,320
Stop.

810
00:41:58,510 --> 00:42:00,440
Can you two please not start talking

811
00:42:00,440 --> 00:42:02,630
