815
00:42:08,400 --> 00:42:10,280
Talking about

816
00:42:10,280 --> 00:42:11,480
marriage all the time.

817
00:42:11,480 --> 00:42:13,320
Will it ever end? So annoying.

818
00:42:14,510 --> 00:42:16,400
My Lady, Master wants to see you.

819
00:42:16,710 --> 00:42:17,510
What for?

820
00:42:18,000 --> 00:42:19,600
To talk about your marriage.

821
00:42:30,190 --> 00:42:32,990
This writing is neither clerical nor
seal script,

822
00:42:35,230 --> 00:42:38,760
but rather resembles the ancient ritual
bronze inscriptions.

823
00:42:42,160 --> 00:42:44,470
What could its meaning be?

824
00:42:56,110 --> 00:42:56,920
Father.

825
00:42:58,440 --> 00:42:59,630
Why do you have this?

826
00:43:00,030 --> 00:43:01,510
What happened to your face?

827
00:43:01,510 --> 00:43:03,510
It's nothing, just a small scratch.

828
00:43:03,590 --> 00:43:05,320
Where did you get this note?

829
00:43:07,710 --> 00:43:09,110
You recognize this?

830
00:43:10,660 --> 00:43:12,610
Word on the street says

831
00:43:12,840 --> 00:43:14,080
this is

832
00:43:14,150 --> 00:43:16,340
the formula for the
method of weapon forging.
